Build essentials:
sudo apt-get install g++ unar cmake libssl-dev zlib1g-dev

Install libraries:
./install.sh

./create.sh commands:
	./create clean	- cleans everying and re-build
	./create run	- builds new code and runs the program
	./create		- just build the new code

FIRST USE:
1. Install build essentials using the command above
2. Install libraries using the command above
3. Compile using ./create.sh
4. Run using ./create.sh run, after adjusting IPs in speaker_ips